{
  "stem": "27770.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mongolian-Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the Russian arrived to Birkenau, one day, the Germans, they came, and they know that all these Russian soldiers could make a lot of trouble.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could even have a fight with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took all of them, two or three days before the Russian arrived to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They was putting them next to the wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They killed them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not one Russian soldier stayed alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They killed them all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] two or three times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Twice I had to go there, because she didn't feel good, and she needed some medicine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came to this hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the doctor-- Jewish doctor woman-- she told me what medicine I should bring.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had all the connection with the doctor, so I brought the medicine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I brought her vitamins.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I brought her clothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could do everything, because I had the opportunity, you understand?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, before, we knew already two or three days before that we're leaving Birkenau, Auschwitz, because we had to move away, an old Polish friends-- they liked me very much because I talked the Hebrew language, and they liked to be with Jews who knows Hebrew-- and they told me, listen, now we have to go away from here, and try to move away from here, because when they made empty camp, they kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 76
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody will stay alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I figured, I have to go away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was the middle of the night I got the information.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew my sister is next door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I couldn't wake her up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't go to next door, so I got, right away, boots, pants, coats, everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had the connection there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I start middle of the night, two o'clock, with stones to knock in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
